Relationship to Compound III (Comet)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
aerarium is a user interface. It interacts with a deployed Compound III (Comet)
money market via that contract's ABI and calldata; it does NOT contain, fork, or
redistribute Compound contract source.

The Comet contracts are maintained as a separate repository:

    https://github.com/rome-protocol/compound-on-rome-comet

which is licensed under the Business Source License 1.1 (BUSL-1.1). Use of those
contracts is governed by that license and its Additional Use Grant — not by this
repository's Apache-2.0 license.

